{"tid":300994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【踢波唔見勞】峰迴路轉！波友地通拿交阿Sir 一過手變A貨","createTime":"2017-06-28T10:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T03:21:49.000Z","uid":23707,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55485b6b063ff5b23ced5eccdf2363b70ea7203b","tid":300994,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170628&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56887578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170628%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56887578&d=XM9Y1UHZQHybt6cAtfxxeMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=33d51fb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170628%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56887578&h=ced2e346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170628&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56887578</a><br />\n【踢波唔見勞】峰迴路轉！波友地通拿交阿Sir 一過手變A貨"},{"pid":"d6062ab848c64bf80a3f334c0fc59dee316fdf12","tid":300994,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"周日晚勞力士迷工程判頭與友人在長沙灣發祥街踢波後，發現價值42萬元的地通拿名錶失竊，6小時後友人報稱「唔小心攞咗隻錶」將名錶交到警署(相關新聞︰ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2te46er\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2te46er&d=XM9Y1UHZQHybt6cAtfxxeMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=424dcad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2te46er</a> )，事情本以為告一段落，可是今日案件又有峰迴路轉新發展，消息指，警方正調查交還的勞士錶曾被調包事件，正向一名涉案警員調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，警方調查發現，誤取事主手錶的友人當日到報案室將名錶交予一名當值警員，至翌日，有警方高層查問事件，該名報案室警員突然「自爆」，報稱辦手續期間遺失名錶後，一度偷龍轉鳳，拿出一隻冒牌A貨暫時「頂替」，至上司查問時才將真錶交出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。警方覺得案件事有蹊蹺，交由重案組調查。"},{"pid":"50c98715741d34ef9ba3b0a4f11555ec54411d8c","tid":300994,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"4日內案件屢有新發展，《蘋果》聯絡到事主鍾先生(20歲)，他稱今早曾去長沙灣警署錄口供，但當時警方未告知有警員被捕，而當日友人交到警署的勞力士手錶現時仍存放於長沙灣警署的證物室夾萬，不過警方今早曾要求他將該隻地通拿手錶的出廠編號出世紙帶到警署助查。<br />\n<br />\n案中失而復得，但又被揭發疑是冒牌貨的是勞力士Cosmograph Daytona（地通拿）116506型號手錶，任職工程判頭的姓鍾事主稱該錶價值43.5萬元，是去年年初他慶祝做成一宗大生意買給自己留念。<br />\n<br />\nCosmograph Daytona（地通拿）採用40mm淺藍鉑金屬表面，配以棕色陶瓷圈及蠔式錶帶，甚具收藏價值。日本紅星木村拓哉，於2015年訪台時，即戴上這款手錶，頓成一時潮物。"},{"pid":"e13e9c36a9ebb74e9735fdbd3bce5358d5457cd2","tid":300994,"uid":81852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"228b029d672854108dfa1681932d015ebaacf8f7","tid":300994,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"三重羅生門"},{"pid":"de15ecb3dd3c9cfab58753f080a95404192e6c4f","tid":300994,"uid":34295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"咁神心去買隻假野？<br />\nA貨都幾千蚊啦"},{"pid":"64e3a443d769bd707af001796fe40377a61aa9f6","tid":300994,"uid":34742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d13398155d2489738b6313c5e083fbc7cc5d04b","tid":300994,"uid":3976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毅進仔+1分</blockquote><br />\n值班警+1分"},{"pid":"af14e4ee8b5a63b68c758b855840b95686926fa8","tid":300994,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bcf088dcc54520270ff2015aeffb12f3db8269","tid":300994,"uid":13492,"like":